		<h1 class="hero-headline">
			Zero-config <em>ephemeral</em> preview&nbsp;environments powered by ddev.
		</h1>

		<hr class="hero-divider">

		<p class="hero-tagline">Send anyone a live preview of exactly what you're seeing. <strong>Multiple branches, all live at once</strong> — no switching, no setup.</p>

		<div class="code-wrap">
			<div class="code-block">
				<span class="prompt">$</span><code>bash &lt;(curl -fsSL mayfly.live/preview.sh)</code>
			</div>
			<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Copy</button>
		</div>

